headline: Trane Technologies Announces New $5 Billion Share Repurchase Program
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, December 09, 2024--The Board of Directors of Trane Technologies plc (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, authorized a new share repurchase program of up to $5 billion, to commence upon the completion of the company’s 2022 $3 billion program. As of October 31, 2024, the 2022 program had approximately $1.5 billion remaining.
